==Tailoring==
Fiddlehead Fern is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create {{name|Shirt007|link=Tailoring{{!}}Green Overalls|class=inline}}. It is a green dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the green dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

Green overalls may reference [[wikipedia:Luigi|Luigi]], from the [[wikipedia:Super_Mario|Super Mario series]]. The description of the overalls also allude to this.

==Quests==
Fiddlehead Fern is not used in any [[quests]].

